video_info.title: 15 MIN FULL BODY EXPRESS HIIT Workout - With Weights, No Repeats, No Talking Home Workout
video_info.description:
Quick & Effective 15-minute HIIT home workout that is going to make you sweat & feel good! Move your body, enjoy some new motivating music, burn calories and have fun! It's with weights, it's super sweaty, and I know you're going to love it Team! Grab your mat & dumbbells, and let's go!

♡ Sign up to my Grow with Anna APP: https://growwithanna.page.link/GetGrowNow

▸ Level: Intermediate
▸ Time: 15 Min
▸ Equipment: With Dumbbells
▸ Workout 50 sec on, 10 sec off

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.
